<!-- TEMPLATE PAGE -->

<div class="content-col clearfix">

    <!-- IMAGE FRAME DOESN'T CHANGE EXCEPT FOR BACKGROUND IMG -->
    <div class="frame-container clearfix">
        <div class="image-frame">
            <div class="stats-bar clearfix">
                <div class="stat-35">
                    Capt Log<br>
                    OT-00<span class="idSpan">{{items.captain_id}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-20 prof">
                    <img height="13px" src="/images/prof_icon.svg">
                    <span>{{items.proficiency_points}}</span>
                    <div class="stat-text hide-prof">Proficiency</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-20 scrap">
                    <img height="12px" src="/images/scrap_icon.svg">
                    <span>{{items.scrap_amount}}</span>
                    <div class="stat-text hide-scrap">Scrap</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-20 crew">
                    <img height="12px" src="/images/crew_icon.svg">
                    <span>{{items.crew_hp}}</span>
                    <div class="stat-text hide-crew">Crew</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="image-box" style="background-image: url('../images/storyimg/4_3.png');"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="frame-container clearfix">
        <div class="text-frame">
            <div class="text-title">
                Rise and shine!
            </div>
            <div class="text-divide"></div>
            <div class="text-body">
                The pods hiss open and fog slowly falls to the deck plate. They thank you for waking them - it seems their pods malfunctioned and were in statis for longer than planned. They mention their original path way to Orion but they're now off course. They could use your help getting back on track and ask to join your crew.
                <br />
                <br />
                Your first mate whispers into your ear, "Captain, we have resources, but enough to take on their whole crew?"
                <br />
                <br />
                How do you respond to their request?
            </div>
            <div class="text-divide"></div>

            <!-- CHANGE DATA-ATTRIBUTES FOR EACH CHOICE // CHANGE DATA-CHAP/DATA-PAGE TO THE NEXT PAGE (SAME FOR EACH BUTTON) -->
            <div data-scrap="-20" data-crew="12" data-prof="0" data-chap="4" data-page="3a" class="option-buttons">
                "If we conserve resources, we should be able to make it home. You are welcome aboard the <span style="color: red;">{{items.ship_name}}</span>"
            </div>
            <div data-scrap="0" data-crew="0" data-prof="0" data-chap="4" data-page="4" class="option-buttons">
                "Sorry, we have no room for freeloaders"
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

